505
00:44:45,320 --> 00:44:48,596
You see. Harry was helping me
answer my fan mail.

506
00:44:48,759 --> 00:44:51,910
That's why Ron and I
went looking for him. professor.

507
00:44:52,079 --> 00:44:54,718
We'd just found him when he said....

508
00:44:56,880 --> 00:45:00,555
-Yes. Miss Granger?
-When I said I wasn't hungry.

509
00:45:01,880 --> 00:45:05,714
We were heading back to the common
room when we found Mrs. Norris.

510
00:45:07,959 --> 00:45:13,272
-|nnocent until proven guilty. Severus.
