When matured. a potion will be made
which will revive Mrs. Norris.

514
00:45:29,880 --> 00:45:31,518
And in the meantime...

515
00:45:32,039 --> 00:45:35,873
...I strongly recommend caution...

516
00:45:36,519 --> 00:45:38,430
...to all.

517
00:45:48,999 --> 00:45:52,309
-|t's a bit strange. isn't it?
-Strange?

518
00:45:52,479 --> 00:45:55,118
You hear this voice.
a voice only you can hear...

519
00:45:55,280 --> 00:45:59,796
...and then Mrs. Norris turns up
Petrified. It's just strange.

520
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:03,077
