Dumbledore and the others. I mean?

521
00:46:03,239 --> 00:46:04,638
Are you mad?

522
00:46:04,800 --> 00:46:10,079
No, Harry. Even in the wizarding world.
hearing voices isn't a good sign.

523
00:46:12,080 --> 00:46:14,355
She's right. you know.

524
00:46:18,519 --> 00:46:20,749
