527
00:46:29,880 --> 00:46:31,472
Like so.

528
00:46:31,640 --> 00:46:36,350
One. two. three.
Vera Verto.

529
00:46:39,759 --> 00:46:43,513
Now it's your turn.
Who would like to go first?

530
00:46:44,080 --> 00:46:48,835
Mr. Weasley.
“One. two. three. Vera Verto.“

531
00:46:52,280 --> 00:46:54,271
Vera Verto!

532
00:47:00,160 --> 00:47:02,720
That wand needs replacing.
Mr. Weasley.

533
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:06,070
-Yes. Miss Granger?
-Professor. ..

534
00:47:06,239 --> 00:47:10,278
...l was wondering if you could tell us
about the Chamber of Secrets.

535
00:47:16,199 --> 00:47:17,393
Very well.

536
00:47:18,839 --> 00:47:20,750
You all know. of course...

537
00:47:20,920 --> 00:47:24,629
...that Hogwarts was founded
over a thousand years ago...

538
00:47:24,799 --> 00:47:29,031
...by the four greatest witches
and wizards of the age:

539
00:47:29,199 --> 00:47:32,794
Godric Gryffindor.
Helga Hufflepuff...

540
00:47:32,959 --> 00:47:38,352
...Rowena Ravenclaw
and Salazar Slytherin.

541
00:47:38,999 --> 00:47:44,756
Now. three of the founders
coexisted quite harmoniously.

542
00:47:44,920 --> 00:47:47,832
-One did not.
-Three guesses who.

543
00:47:48,519 --> 00:47:50,874
Salazar Slytherin wished to be
more selective...

544
