the Muggle-borns in the school by then.

591
00:50:46,839 --> 00:50:48,670
I know.

592
00:50:48,839 --> 00:50:51,558
But it's the only plan we've got.

593
00:51:39,199 --> 00:51:41,793
Another goal for Slytherin!

594
00:51:43,159 --> 00:51:46,310
They lead Gryffindor 90 to 30.

595
00:51:47,440 --> 00:51:48,953
Yeah!

596
00:51:49,199 --> 00:51:50,917
Yeah!

