00:57:15,199 --> 00:57:16,188
Hello.

631
00:57:17,920 --> 00:57:18,909
Dobby?

632
00:57:19,079 --> 00:57:21,309
Harry Potter should have listened
to Dobby.

633
00:57:21,759 --> 00:57:25,308
Harry Potter should have gone back home
when he missed the train.

634
00:57:25,480 --> 00:57:29,917
It was you. You stopped the barrier
from letting Ron and me through.

635
00:57:30,199 --> 00:57:33,032
lndeed. Yes. sir.

636
00:57:33,999 --> 00:57:38,834
-You nearly got Ron and me expelled.
-At least you would be away from here.

637
00:57:39,000 --> 00:57:41,560
Harry Potter must go home.

638
00:57:41,720 --> 00:57:45,156
Dobby thought his Bludger would be
enough to make Harry Potter see--

639
00:57:45,319 --> 00:57:48,550
Your Bludger? You made
that Bludger chase after me?

640
00:57:48,720 --> 00:57:52,156
Dobby feels most aggrieved. sir.

641
00:57:52,320 --> 00:57:55,790
Dobby had to iron his hands.

642
00:57:57,920 --> 00:58:02,311
You better clear off before my bones
come back. or I might strangle you.

643
00:58:04,839 --> 00:58:06,750
Dobby is used to death threats. sir.

644
00:58:06,920 --> 00:58:09,832
Dobby gets them five times a day
at home.

645
00:58:09,999 --> 00:58:12,672
I don't suppose you could tell me
why you're trying to kill me?

646
00:58:12,960 --> 00:58:16,669
Not kill you. sir.
Never kill you.

647
00:58:16,839 --> 00:58:20,036
Dobby remembers how it was
before Harry Potter triumphed...

648
00:58:20,200 --> 00:58:23,192
...over He-Who-Must-Not-Be-Named.

649
00:58:23,360 --> 00:58:26,909
We house-elves were
treated like vermin. sir.

650
00:58:27,079 --> 00:58:32,278
Of course. Dobby is still
treated like vermin.

651
00:58:41,239 --> 00:58:43,753
Why do you wear that thing. Dobby?

652
00:58:43,920 --> 00:58:48,835
This. sir? It is a mark
of the house-elf's enslavement.

653
00:58:49,000 --> 00:58:53,915
Dobby can only be freed if his master
presents him with clothes.

654
00:58:55,960 --> 00:58:57,279
Listen.

655
00:58:57,439 --> 00:58:58,918
Listen!

656
00:58:59,079 --> 00:59:02,628
Terrible things are
about to happen at Hogwarts.

657
00:59:03,239 --> 00:59:05,594
Harry Potter must not stay here...

658
00:59:05,760 --> 00:59:10,117
...now that history
is to repeat itself.

659
00:59:10,279 --> 00:59:13,589
Repeat itself? You mean
this has happened before?

660
00:59:13,760 --> 00:59:15,671
I shouldn't have said that.

661
00:59:19,240 --> 00:59:22,277
-Bad Dobby! Bad!
-Stop it!

662
00:59:22,439 --> 00:59:24,031
Stop it. Dobby!

663
00:59:25,639 --> 00:59:29,314
Tell me. When did this happen before?
Who's doing it now?

664
00:59:29,480 --> 00:59:34,474
Dobby cannot say. sir. Dobby
only wants Harry Potter to be safe.

665
00:59:34,640 --> 00:59:37,438
No. Dobby. Tell me.
Who is it?

666
00:59:48,800 --> 00:59:49,835
Put him here.

667
00:59:54,239 --> 00:59:57,037
-What happened?
-There's been another attack.

668
00:59:57,199 --> 01:00:02,751
I think he's been Petrified.
Madam Pomfrey.

669
01:00:03,520 --> 01:00:08,036
Look. Perhaps he managed
to take a picture of his attacker.

670
01:00:15,799 --> 01:00:18,438
What can this mean. Albus?

671
01:00:18,600 --> 01:00:20,477
It means...

672
01:00:20,839 --> 01:00:23,478
...that our students
are in great danger.

673
01:00:23,639 --> 01:00:26,915
-What should I tell the staff?
-The truth.

674
01:00:27,159 --> 01:00:30,788
Tell them Hogwarts
is no longer safe.

675
01:00:31,120 --> 01:00:33,953
It is as we feared. Minerva.

676
01:00:34,199 --> 01:00:38,556
The Chamber of Secrets
has indeed been opened again.

677
01:00:41,279 --> 01:00:45,238
Again? You mean the Chamber
of Secrets has been opened before?

678
01:00:45,400 --> 01:00:48,039
Of course.
Don't you see?

679
01:00:48,199 --> 01:00:51,077
Lucius Malfoy must have opened it
when he was at school here.

680
01:00:51,680 --> 01:00:54,148
-Now he's taught Draco how to do it.
-Maybe.

681
01:00:54,319 --> 01:00:57,356
We'll have to wait for
the Polyjuice Potion to know for sure.

682
01:00:57,520 --> 01:01:01,308
Enlighten me. Why are we brewing
this potion in broad daylight...

683
01:01:01,480 --> 01:01:05,268
...in the middle of the girls' lavatory?
Don't you think we'll get caught?

684
01:01:06,119 --> 01:01:08,679
No. No one ever comes in here.

685
01:01:09,480 --> 01:01:11,914
-Why?
-Moaning Myrtle.

686
01:01:12,080 --> 01:01:13,957
Who?

687
01:01:14,440 --> 01:01:16,032
Moaning Myrtle.

688
01:01:16,319 --> 01:01:19,516
-Who's Moaning Myrtle?
-|'m Moaning Myrtle.

689
01:01:25,200 --> 01:01:27,475
